---
title: Creamy Chicken, Bacon & Mushroom Boscaiola with Fettuccine & Rocket Almond Salad
description: When the craving for a creamy pasta dish hits there’s only one solution - a boscaiola. Soft and warming, it will fill up your belly
with love from the hearty mushrooms and chicken stirred through the creamy sauce. Pasta has never looked better than this!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64facfff0b237e7ffbabcb69-c7d528c4.jpeg
